</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[133,1122,1796,1825]" pageId="103" pageNumber="381" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="103.[133,1337,1367,1984]" box="[133,1122,1796,1825]" pageId="103" pageNumber="381">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[133,367,1796,1825]" pageId="103" pageNumber="381">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Santa Cruz Deermouse is presumably nocturnal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
